FBIS3-12709 "drnes043_j_94010" FBIS-NES-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen YRG Denies Complicity in Abyan Incidents JN2702163994 Baghdad INA in Arabic 1230 GMT 27 Feb 94 JN2702163994 Baghdad INA Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Sanaa, 27 Feb (INA)- A source at the Yemeni Reform Grouping [YRG], one of the three ruling coalition parties in Yemen, has denied reports of its complicity in military incidents that occurred in the Yemeni Governorate of Abyan last Monday. In a statement to the press in Sanaa last night, the source asserted that the YRG has never been a party in any bloody military dispute among the sons of Yemen. Press reports had accused the grouping of sending armed men to escalate the military incidents against the Yemeni Socialist Party's supporters in the Abyan Governorate.
